Summary: Very WHITE object over Toms River, NJ
divs: Sighting DetailsWalking into day progam, and was looking up at daytime moon and checking forChemtrails is what made me notice object. I was totally enthralled as iwas FINALLY observing a UFO and afterward i am still thinking about it someeven though it was by no means a close encounter. The object appeared ascylindrical from side view that i thought i was observing. Very intenselywhite in color and about 1cm in lenght and perhaps 1-2mm in width.Object traveled in straight line in and out of clouds till i lost sight of itbehind a clould to the north.
